definition:
A man living at the time of United Monarchy, first mentioned at 1Sa.21.10; 
 son of: Maoch (H4582); also called Abimelech (NIV: Abimelek) at Psa.34.1; 
Also named: a.vi.me.lekh (אֲבִימֶ֫לֶךְ "Abimelech" H0040I) 
 § Achish = "I will blacken (or terrify)" or "only a man"
 Philistine king of Gath
